{"word":"G2551 - κακολογέω - kakologéō - kak-ol-og-eh'-o - Curse","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κακολογέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>kakologéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>kak-ol-og-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Curse"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நிந்தி, தீங்குசொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. to speak ill of, revile, abuse, one; to calumniate, traduce"},{"paragraph":"2. to imprecate evil on, curse"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From a compound of <a href=\"#/G2556 - κακός - kakós - kak-os'/2556\">G2556</a> nad <a href=\"#/G3056 - λόγος - lógos - log'-os/3056\">G3056</a>; to <i>revile:</i> - curse, speak evil of."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}